{"tid":1573136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院今日會就是否頒令港鐵披露CCTV紀錄進行指示聆訊","createTime":"2019-09-16T01:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T08:40:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e4bf056019cdc8428643edc6fff845af1f3390","tid":1573136,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"申請人梁耀霆，答辯人香港鐵路有限公司。原告根據《高等法院規則》第42條及第24號命令第7A條規則，申請原訴傳票，要求答辯人向代表原告的律師行披露2019年8月31日晚上9時半至翌日凌晨1時45分位於港鐵太子站的所有閉路電視紀綠，以及2019年9月1日凌晨12時30分至凌晨2時位於港鐵荔枝角站所有閉路電視紀錄，以供代表律師檢查及保存副本，並要求答辯人須於法庭頒令起7天內盡快執行有關命令。<br />\n<br />\n根據司法機構網頁顯示，高等法院將於下周一(16日)早上9時半就是次申請進行法庭指示聆訊，主審法官為周家明，估計需時30分鐘。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2448255/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2448255%2F&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xamkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=c976ea2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2448255/</a>"},{"pid":"0e59e19c6e218981004cb0a08df0c8fa8909b6b8","tid":1573136,"uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"最驚有中共勢力介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918a869740b5bdcab62bd76899565303115e9d13","tid":1573136,"uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"判一地兩檢司法覆核敗訴 接納大陸專家意見 法官周家明：人大常委決定約束港法院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗審都估到點判"},{"pid":"e6a4f35f132f1958d0cfb0a347a649783ea9d987","tid":1573136,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"周家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52674e66fd52ab89e77fe470976b57b0ecf0f84","tid":1573136,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04d5a563d0477bb530970cf017c43aaf99ea655","tid":1573136,"uid":195540,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyT